[00:51.35]	Signior Baptista, you are happily met.
[00:53.95]	[To the Pedant]
[00:54.68]	Sir, this is the gentleman I told you of:
[00:57.46]	I pray you stand good father to me now,
[01:00.18]	Give me Bianca for my patrimony.
